# MCP Server Assignments for ic-knowledge-graph

This project uses two MCP servers. Always use these and no others when performing
ArangoDB operations or entity resolution tasks within this workspace.

## ArangoDB (graph database operations, AQL queries)

**Server name:** `user-arangodb-ic-knowledge-graph-mcp`

Use this for:
- AQL queries against the `ic-knowledge-graph-temporal` database
- Collection inspection, document CRUD, index management
- Graph traversals over `IC_Temporal_Knowledge_Graph`

## Entity Resolution

**Server name:** `user-ic-knowledge-graph-arango-entity-resolution-mcp`

Use this for:
- Finding duplicate records or resolving entities
- Explaining why two records match / were rejected
- Managing entity clusters

## Never use for this project

- `user-arangodb-dnb-sharded-amp-mcp` — DNB dataset, different database
- `user-arangodb-fraud-intelligence-mcp` — fraud intelligence graph
- `user-arangodb-risk-intelligence-mcp` — risk intelligence graph
- `user-dnb-er` — DNB entity resolution
- `user-fraud-intelligence-arango-entity-resolution-mcp` — fraud ER
- `user-entity-resolution-demo` — demo instance
